# ============================================================
# R and RStudio files
# ============================================================
.Rhistory
.RData
.Ruserdata
.Rproj.user/
*.Rproj
*.RData
*.rds
*.RDS

# ============================================================
# Raw and sensitive data
# Do not upload fisher-level survey data, GPS coordinates, or raw field files.
# Keep only data/README.md on GitHub.
# ============================================================
data/*.csv
data/*.xlsx
data/*.xls
data/*.RData
data/*.rds
data/*.RDS
!data/README.md

# ============================================================
# Temporary files
# ============================================================
*.tmp
*.temp
*.log

# ============================================================
# Operating system files
# ============================================================
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ============================================================
# Keep outputs visible
# The repository may include selected summary tables and figures.
# If you later want to hide generated figures or tables, uncomment these:
#
# outputs/figures/*
# outputs/tables/*
# !outputs/figures/.gitkeep
# !outputs/tables/.gitkeep
# ============================================================
